      "rationale": "All three FEA platforms (FDA in-house code, Ansys 2022 R2, DePuy Synthes solver) operate under documented QA frameworks with version control and regression testing. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for a Medium model risk COU."
    },
    {
